Name: To The Capital 2
About the game: To The Capital 2 is a game in the genre jRPG with classic turn-based battles in which you have to travel together with four heroes visiting a lot of cities, dungeons, mysterious places and fight with various bosses. Storyline Preventing the overthrow of the current authorities and getting to the capital, Luis receives a task from the king to find fugitive participants in the failed coup. Together with Ralph, Bernard and Amelia joined on the orders of the command, they start a journey.
